Localization.Name: Testudo Legs Earthshake
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Medium Armor
Damage Reduction: 30%
Temp. Rating: -50 / 80 °C
Radiation Protection: 26400 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 145.8 REM/s
Carrying Capacity: 4K µSCU

The Testudo armor for Quirinus Tech blends battlefield durability with everyday comfort. It weaves tough, yet lightweight, plating with ultra-strong synthetic fibers to provide premium protection. Lining the inside is a proprietary micromodal fabric that's soft to the touch and wicks away moisture for supreme comfort.
